-login process was unified in **tik4net 3.5.0** (see [History](History)), those constants are **obsolete and
-removed from use** — `Api` / `ApiSsl` handle both. Replace any `Api_v2` / `ApiSsl_v2` in old code with
+Earlier tik4net versions exposed separate `Api_v2` / `ApiSsl_v2` constants for the 6.43+ login. The login
